[URL=http://s619.photobucket.com/user/hop_04/media/etalyx/soul_zps74cdb003.png.html][IMG]http://i619.photobucket.com/albums/tt275/hop_04/etalyx/soul_zps74cdb003.png[/img][/URL] [URL=http://s619.photobucket.com/user/hop_04/media/etalyx/talk1_zpse369d7e3.jpg.html][IMG]http://i619.photobucket.com/albums/tt275/hop_04/etalyx/talk1_zpse369d7e3.jpg[/img][/URL] [URL=http://s619.photobucket.com/user/hop_04/media/etalyx/talk2_zps16e64441.jpg.html][IMG]http://i619.photobucket.com/albums/tt275/hop_04/etalyx/talk2_zps16e64441.jpg[/img][/URL] Prestige and receive equipment that gains charges. Once full, deplete its charges to upgrade your equipment or for rewards.
[URL=http://s619.photobucket.com/user/hop_04/media/etalyx/5_zps226e1560.jpg.html][IMG]http://i619.photobucket.com/albums/tt275/hop_04/etalyx/5_zps226e1560.jpg[/img][/URL]

Prestige and unlock access to Soul Charging, new head icons that are toggable, custom titles, and equipment upgrading for PvM purposes.
[URL=http://s619.photobucket.com/user/hop_04/media/etalyx/mini_zps557814d6.png.html][IMG]http://i619.photobucket.com/albums/tt275/hop_04/etalyx/mini_zps557814d6.png[/img][/URL] [URL=http://s619.photobucket.com/user/hop_04/media/etalyx/4_zpsa48c50d9.jpg.html][IMG]http://i619.photobucket.com/albums/tt275/hop_04/etalyx/4_zpsa48c50d9.jpg[/img][/URL] [URL=http://s619.photobucket.com/user/hop_04/media/etalyx/6_zpsa1b30ebe.jpg.html][IMG]http://i619.photobucket.com/albums/tt275/hop_04/etalyx/6_zpsa1b30ebe.jpg[/img][/URL]

Collect certain items that can be exchanged in for a key which then can be used to take a shot at getting exotic cosmetic equips.
[URL=http://s619.photobucket.com/user/hop_04/media/etalyx/SET4_zps179ca627.jpg.html][IMG]http://i619.photobucket.com/albums/tt275/hop_04/etalyx/SET4_zps179ca627.jpg[/img][/URL][URL=http://s619.photobucket.com/user/hop_04/media/etalyx/SET2_zpsabb085cf.jpg.html][IMG]http://i619.photobucket.com/albums/tt275/hop_04/etalyx/SET2_zpsabb085cf.jpg[/img][/URL][URL=http://s619.photobucket.com/user/hop_04/media/etalyx/SET1_zps4c086c92.jpg.html][IMG]http://i619.photobucket.com/albums/tt275/hop_04/etalyx/SET1_zps4c086c92.jpg[/img][/URL]
